<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>INDEX — 한국실내건축가협회</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" crossorigin />
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.css"
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-1: #eef1fb;
      --bg-2: #e8ecf8;
      --bg-3: #f3f1fb;
      --ink: #1f2533;
      --ink-soft: #6b7280;
      --ink-faint: #9ca3af;
      --accent: #4f6bf6;
      --accent-soft: #93a8fb;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --footer: #181b27;
      --footer-link: #9aa3b2;
      --line: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.07);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html, body { height: 100%; }

    body {
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
        "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--bg-2);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── Header ───────────────────────────── */
    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 56px;
      padding: 22px 24px;
      background: rgba(238, 241, 251, 0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }
    header a {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: -0.2px;
      color: #4b5563;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s ease;
    }
    header a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── Hero ─────────────────────────────── */
    main {
      flex: 1;
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 24px 120px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(1100px 600px at 18% 8%, var(--bg-3) 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(1000px 620px at 82% 30%, #e7edfb 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(900px 700px at 60% 95%, #eef0fb 0%, transparent 60%),
        linear-gradient(160deg, var(--bg-1) 0%, var(--bg-2) 100%);
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -1.2px;
      color: var(--ink);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* ── Search card ──────────────────────── */
    .search {
      margin-top: 56px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 560px;
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(80, 100, 200, 0.10);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .search-top {
      position: relative;
      padding: 22px 22px 18px;
      min-height: 92px;
    }
    .search-input {
      width: 100%;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: transparent;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }
    .search-input::placeholder { color: #9aa1ad; }

    .search-tools {
      position: absolute;
      right: 18px;
      bottom: 14px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .icon-btn {
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background 0.15s ease;
    }
    .icon-btn:hover { background: #eef1fe; }
    .icon-btn svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }

    .search-bottom {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .chips { display: flex; gap: 18px; }
    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #6b7280;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      letter-spacing: -0.2px;
      transition: color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .chip:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .chip svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

    .send {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
    }
    .send:hover { background: var(--accent); }
    .send:active { transform: scale(0.94); }
    .send svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }

    /* ── Footer ───────────────────────────── */
    footer {
      background: var(--footer);
      color: #cdd3df;
    }
    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 48px 40px 28px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .brand .logo {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .brand .org {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--footer-link);
    }
    .fcol h4 {
      display: none; /* original groups have no visible heading */
    }
    .fcol ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .fcol a {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--footer-link);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .fcol a:hover { color: #fff; }

    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 18px 40px 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    }
    .footer-bottom .copy { font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
    .footer-bottom nav { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .footer-bottom nav a {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--footer-link);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer-bottom nav a:hover { color: #fff; }
    .footer-bottom nav span { color: #3a3f4d; font-size: 11px; }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .hero-title { font-size: 38px; }
      header { gap: 28px; }
      .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <a href="#">케이스 라이브러리</a>
    <a href="#">세미나</a>
    <a href="#">마이페이지</a>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h1 class="hero-title">INDEX</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">인테리어 공사 정보, 검색으로 시작하세요.</p>

    <form class="search" onsubmit="return false;">
      <div class="search-top">
        <input class="search-input" type="text" placeholder="무엇이든 물어보세요" />
        <div class="search-tools">
          <button type="button" class="icon-btn" aria-label="추가">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" /></svg>
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="icon-btn" aria-label="음성 검색">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="9" y="3" width="6" height="11" rx="3" />
              <path d="M5 11a7 7 0 0 0 14 0M12 18v3" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="search-bottom">
        <div class="chips">
          <button type="button" class="chip">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M4 6h16M7 12h10M10 18h4" /></svg>
            필터
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="chip">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M3 3v5h5" />
              <path d="M3.05 13A9 9 0 1 0 6 5.3L3 8" />
              <path d="M12 7v5l3 2" />
            </svg>
            최근 검색
          </button>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="send" aria-label="검색">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"
            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" /></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="logo">INDEX</div>
        <div class="org">한국실내건축가협회</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fcol">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">협회 소개</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">인사말</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">조직 안내</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">연혁</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="fcol">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">하자 정보</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">하자 유형</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">사례 데이터베이스</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">표준 지침</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="fcol">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">고객 지원</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">공지사항</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">자주 묻는 질문</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">문의하기</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <div class="copy">© 2025 한국실내건축가협회 (K-IAA). All rights reserved.</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#">개인정보처리방침</a>
        <span>|</span>
        <a href="#">이용약관</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
